What you need to know:

However, chasing the title along with Indiza will be Vet Lab’s Edwin Mudanyi, Kenya Railway Golf Club’s Samuel Njoroge, Golf Park’s David Wakhu and Eric Ooko, Muthaiga’s Greg Snow, Sigona’s John Wangai, and the Great Rift Valley Golf Resort’s Justus Madoya among others.The Uganda Open is part of the Safari Tour, hence besides the cash, players will also be chasing some points towards the “Road to 2021 Magical Kenya Open’’ to be held at Karen Country Club.